Message.Text: Im sorry, I shouldn't be laying this on you, but my clock says AM and I need to talk to someone
im glad u changed ur msn name btw
shouldnt it be understandable that stuff like that would happen in ur 2? 3? year relationship?
To no why something is absurd, makes it no longer absurd at all
I dont set out to do something for honor... I mean sure I'll pick the rubbish up cuz its the right thing to do
but wen U said "and thats good on u for being so supportive", it made me cringe sorta
thankyou for being so great to sonny even thou u dint set out to be
yeah thanks 4 being u basically hah
I didn't ignore that... It was a big fact
and theres heaps of other things too
(like we decided early on we wouldn't, she promised her mum, her mums a MIDWIFE! (argh))
and honestly, I dont think I could ever look her parents in the eye if I had sex...
but, I suppose, when I thought of that something else, it became clear to me
or atleast, was one of the things that my mind travelling at a billion miles an hour could comprehend as a, limit if u will
sorry this probably makes little sense
Hay is there anything U wanna talk about? I
I been gushing on my bullshit for ages
well I suppose I can genuine thank you for that one
but really, is there anything on bethany's mind? something u wanna talk
I feel like a whore If I spend the whole time talking about myself
surely theres gotta be something so fucked up that it spends half your existance driving you nuts just thinking about it?
my whole life is like .. school
Well wat about wats not immediately available?
Do you know wat u wanna do?
wat uni, wat direction? where u want to travel, wat u want to experience, wat path u wanna go down, wat u wan to create, wat mark u want to leave on the world, social life after school
do speech pathology or media and communications
I hate to ask but, thats GOTTA hurt
(I attended that btw in like year 3)
I truely have no idea wat pathology means
it will hurt, but im determined
I mean in year 3 or 4 or watever, reading Dr Seus books out loud to ur parents can be quite a humbling experience...
ha my patients r sooo gunna do that!
I can now sucessfully say "Roger Ramjet Slipped Sideways"
Are u scared tho? for it all?
leaving school, the ultimate security blanket?
Pardon the french but Im scared as all fucking shit
Well, I suppose early entry will change that (if I get in)
but u no, geting exam results back, Uni, leaving friends,
Its just weird to think that people I see everyday I may never see ever again,
you no, makes u wonder, wat regrets Im gonner have, wat Im gonner miss, all that sorta stuff
but dont u hate it all so much now?
i find it scary that we have no control
and we have to keep moving forward
like when u get on a ride at an amusement park
u get locked in and have to stay there
thats so scary that once u sit theres no escape
and u dont get time to just stop... n chill out
and go down and talk to that person you haven't really spoken to in years
Although, on the plus side, I suppose that would be now, huh?
i havent spoken to u like since yr 9?
Takes years to conquer some fears
U became scary after a stupid series of MSN-events, when everyone and their dog new that I was crazeh about u
and after that, I suppose its just a comfort thing, hard to go back to openly talk with someone
we used to talk like allll the time
haha, dont say that like I'd forget bethany:P
far-out, those where the days huh
i never thought u liked me bak
I believe theres too many apologies that cood go into the mistakes I made back then
But, It was fun, ye know
Im a sucker for a good quote, but I believe the movie the beach blew me away with its final sorta summary quote
"I still believe in paradise... But now atleast I know Its not where you go, its how you feel for a moment in your life, and if you find that moment... it will last forever"
I s'pose its one of the things that also convinced me against christianity (but thats a WHOLE nother can o' worms)..
.. but its something I always remember
Just like, moments, love, happyiness, all that business, is eternal,
wats that got to do with christianity? (aint opening ur can, jus wondering)

umm, well I'll mearly read the label of said canned good, but the idea of christianity and most religion, is eternal life, regardless of believes, morals, watever, its the fact of life after death right, well I spose to me, I dont like to think of it like that, because I think Ultimately if u focus your life on the afterlife, you can miss the life you have hear... This is Heaven
but another great quote from the movie Big Fish... "Its rude to talk about religion, you never know who your going to offend", sorta applies
lol its rude not to talk about religion!

Its just something thats sorta bubbled to the surface of the years, Im not saying that a christian can't live, nor someone who is not religious IS living... But for me, its just a truth that I spose defines the way i like to view the world, ya no
Do u think its utter bollocks
oh and im not saying yep to it being bollocks
A philosophy is only as good as the belief in it
well i think i shud go coz im feelin quite sick
its been nice chatting to ya
The mens room calls for me also,
and I suppose sleep is a customary human responce at this hour in the morning
so I may aswell grab some
if yah ever need to talk?
yeh, thanks for the chat, was... nice, I dont really talk to girls that aren't Alison all that much
I used to talk 2 jess heaps, but not so much nowadays
I suppose we didn't actually talk alnight ...

(I made an illusive comment about my dreams, during the anime recount internet thing)
yup, I think thats about all my conffesions I can fit in an evening
